data.name: FGT_Provision_Hub_100F
data.script:
##Hostname
config system global
    set admintimeout 60
    set hostname $(branch_name)
    set timezone 12
    set gui-theme mariner
end

##Admin PW
config sys admin
     edit admin
     set password fortinet
end

##Interface config
config system interface
    edit "wan1"
        set vdom "root"
        set type physical
        set mode static
        set ip $(wan1_ip) $(wan1_mask)
        set allowaccess ping https ssh fgfm
        set alias "wan1"
    next
    edit "wan2"
        set vdom "root"
        set type physical
        set mode static
        set ip $(wan2_ip) $(wan2_mask)
        set allowaccess ping https ssh fgfm
        set alias "wan2"
    next
    edit "lan"
        set vdom "root"
        set type physical
        set mode static
        set ip $(lan_ip) $(lan_mask)
        set allowaccess ping https ssh fgfm
        set alias "lan1"
        set role lan
    next        
    edit "loopback.root"
        set vdom "root"
        set type loopback
        set ip $(mgmt_ip) 255.255.255.255
        set allowaccess ping https ssh fgfm
        set alias "mgmt"
    next  
end


##DHCP
config system dhcp server
    edit 0
        set ntp-service local
        set default-gateway $(lan_ip)
        set netmask $(lan_mask)
        set interface "lan"
        config ip-range
            edit 1
                set start-ip $(lan_ip:4,100)
                set end-ip $(lan_ip:4,199)
            next
        end
    next
end



## VPN Config
## Replaced with Central VPN Manager

##Static Routes
config router static
   edit 500
       set gateway $(wan1_gateway)
       set device "wan1"
    next
    edit 501
        set gateway $(wan2_gateway)
        set device "wan2"
    next    
end

## BGP # Filter prefixes on the Hub to remove duplicates routes on spokes

config router prefix-list
    edit "PL_OL_INET"
        config rule
            edit 1
                set prefix 0.0.0.0 255.255.255.255
                unset ge
                unset le
            next
            edit 2
                set prefix 10.190.1.0 255.255.255.0
                unset ge
                set le 32
            next
        end
    next

    edit "PL_OL_MPLS"
        config rule
            edit 1
                set prefix 0.0.0.0 255.255.255.255
                unset ge
                unset le
            next
            edit 2
                set prefix 10.190.2.0 255.255.255.0
                unset ge
                set le 32
            next
        end
    next
end

config router route-map
    edit "RM_OUT_OL_INET"
        config rule
            edit 1
                set match-ip-nexthop "PL_OL_INET"
            next
            edit 2
                set action deny
            next
        end
    next
    edit "RM_OUT_OL_MPLS"
        config rule
            edit 1
                set match-ip-nexthop "PL_OL_MPLS"
            next
            edit 2
                set action deny
            next
        end
    next
end



##BGP Standard Routing with Multiple paths enabled.

config router bgp
    set as 65599
    set router-id $(mgmt_ip)
    set ibgp-multipath enable
    set additional-path enable
    set additional-path-select 4
    set scan-time 5
    set graceful-restart enable


    config neighbor-group
        edit "OL_MPLS"
            set advertisement-interval 1
            set ebgp-enforce-multihop enable
            set link-down-failover enable
            set soft-reconfiguration enable
            set remote-as 65599
            set keep-alive-timer 1
            set holdtime-timer 3
            set additional-path both
            set route-reflector-client enable
            set next-hop-self enable
            set route-map-out "RM_OUT_OL_MPLS"
        next
        edit "OL_INET"
            set advertisement-interval 1
            set ebgp-enforce-multihop enable
            set link-down-failover enable
            set soft-reconfiguration enable
            set remote-as 65599
            set additional-path both
            set route-reflector-client enable
            set keep-alive-timer 1
            set holdtime-timer 3
            set next-hop-self enable
            set route-map-out "RM_OUT_OL_INET"
        next
    end
    
    config neighbor-range
        edit 1
            set prefix 10.190.1.1 255.255.255.0
            set neighbor-group "OL_INET"
        next
        edit 2
            set prefix 10.190.2.1 255.255.255.0
            set neighbor-group "OL_MPLS"
        next
    end

    config network
        edit 5000
            set prefix $(lan_ip:4,0) $(lan_mask)
        next
        edit 5001
            set prefix $(mgmt_ip) 255.255.255.255
        next
    end

end


# Turn off GUI whats new
config system admin
    edit "admin"
       unset gui-ignore-release-overview-version
    next
 end

data.name: FGT_Provision_Hub_100F_Post
data.script:
##Hostname
config vpn ipsec phase1-interface
  edit OL_MPLS_0
    set tunnel-search nexthop
    set auto-discovery-sender enable
  next
  edit OL_INET_0
    set tunnel-search nexthop
    set auto-discovery-sender enable
  next
 end

data.name: FGT_Provision_Spoke_40F-3G4G
data.script:
##Hostname
config system global
    set admintimeout 60
    set hostname $(branch_name)
    set timezone 12
end

##Admin PW
config sys admin
     edit admin
     set password fortinet
end

##Interface config
config system interface
    edit "wan"
        set vdom "root"
        set type physical
        set mode static
        set ip $(wan1_ip) $(wan1_mask)
        set allowaccess ping https ssh fgfm
        set alias "wan1"
    next

    edit "internal"
        set vdom "root"
        set mode static
        set ip $(lan_ip) $(lan_mask)
        set allowaccess ping https ssh fgfm
        set alias "lan1"
        set role lan
    next 

    edit "loopback.root"
        set vdom "root"
        set type loopback
        set ip $(mgmt_ip) 255.255.255.255
        set allowaccess ping
        set alias "mgmt"
    next    
end



##DHCP
config system dhcp server
    edit 0
        set ntp-service local
        set default-gateway $(lan_ip)
        set netmask $(lan_mask)
        set dns-server1 8.8.8.8
        set dns-server2 8.8.4.4
        set interface "lan"
        config ip-range
            edit 1
                set start-ip $(lan_ip:4,100)
                set end-ip $(lan_ip:4,199)
            next
        end
    next
end



## VPN Config
## Replaced with Central VPN Manager

##Static Routes
config router static
    edit 500
        set gateway $(wan1_gateway)
        set device "wan"
    next
end



##BGP
config router bgp
    set as 65599
    set ibgp-multipath enable
    set network-import-check disable
    config neighbor
        edit "10.190.1.1"
            set link-down-failover enable
            set remote-as 65599
            set connect-timer 10
            set additional-path receive
        next
        edit "10.190.2.1"
            set link-down-failover enable
            set remote-as 65599
            set connect-timer 10
            set additional-path receive
        next
        edit "10.190.3.1"
            set link-down-failover enable
            set remote-as 65599
            set connect-timer 10
            set additional-path receive
        next
        edit "10.190.4.1"
            set link-down-failover enable
            set remote-as 65599
            set connect-timer 10
            set additional-path receive
        next
    end

    config network
        edit 5000
            set prefix $(lan_ip:4,0) $(lan_mask)
        next
        edit 5001
            set prefix $(mgmt_ip) 255.255.255.255
        next
    end

end

# Enable zero touch deployment of Switches and APs
config system interface
    edit "fortilink"
        set auto-auth-extension-device enable
   next
end

# Turn off GUI whats new
config system admin
    edit "admin"
       unset gui-ignore-release-overview-version
    next
 end

data.description: Used to overwrite Opening Hours Schedule per device from Policy Package
data.name: Set_Schedule
data.script:
config firewall schedule recurring
    edit "OpeningHours"
        set start $(opentime)
        set end $(closetime)
        set day monday tuesday wednesday thursday friday
    next
end
